01:28:19.011 --> 01:28:20.446
What happened, Marshall?

1085
01:28:24.950 --> 01:28:26.719
This case
is gonna go to trial.


1086
01:28:28.421 --> 01:28:29.689
No, it won't.

1087
01:28:31.023 --> 01:28:32.290
I'm gonna plead guilty.

1088
01:28:35.528 --> 01:28:38.597
And the judge
will sentence you right there.


1089
01:28:39.364 --> 01:28:40.833
This is premeditated murder.

1090
01:28:42.168 --> 01:28:43.436
30 years to life.

1091
01:28:45.671 --> 01:28:47.305
You will never
see daylight again.


1092
01:28:49.508 --> 01:28:51.811
-I know all this.
-So why are you doing it?


1093
01:29:00.853 --> 01:29:02.388
If there is
reasonable doubt about you,


1094
01:29:02.521 --> 01:29:05.558
if the judge thinks
that in any way


1095
01:29:05.691 --> 01:29:07.526
you are
covering for Samuel...


1096
01:29:08.461 --> 01:29:09.762
he will stay the conviction...

1097
01:29:12.230 --> 01:29:13.532
the investigation
will continue


1098
01:29:13.666 --> 01:29:16.102
and I will have to go
after your son.


1099
01:29:16.234 --> 01:29:17.503
Do you understand me?

1100
01:29:21.339 --> 01:29:22.641
[sniffs]

1101
01:29:26.779 --> 01:29:28.380
Okay.
So that's how it is?


1102
01:29:31.417 --> 01:29:32.685
Yeah. I guess.

1103
01:29:40.693 --> 01:29:41.961
I'm sorry, Marshall.

