1113
01:30:27.139 --> 01:30:28.207
What are you doing?

1114
01:30:28.339 --> 01:30:29.608
[intercom door buzzer buzzing]

1115
01:30:29.742 --> 01:30:31.443
He wanted this to happen.

1116
01:30:33.479 --> 01:30:35.548
I told you,
he is a murderer.


1117
01:30:35.681 --> 01:30:37.283
He is nothing
but a murderer.


1118
01:30:37.416 --> 01:30:39.552
How do-- how do you expect
