1121
01:30:49.662 --> 01:30:51.530
I won't let you ruin your life.

1122
01:30:52.665 --> 01:30:54.300
Dad, Dad, don't do this.

1123
01:30:54.433 --> 01:30:56.068
No, I've made my decision.
The arraignment is tomorrow.


1124
01:30:56.202 --> 01:30:57.335
-I won't fight it.
-Dad-- dad, listen-- listen.


1125
01:30:57.469 --> 01:30:59.138
[Marshall] I'm done.

1126
01:30:59.271 --> 01:31:00.906
[intercom door buzzer buzzing]

1127
