My folks raised me Catholic.

1137
01:32:13.245 --> 01:32:16.081
I sat in pew every Sunday
until I made confirmation.


1138
01:32:17.716 --> 01:32:20.052
It was the first thing to go
when I went to college.


1139
01:32:21.921 --> 01:32:24.123
"A lapsed Catholic
is a good Catholic,"


1140
01:32:24.256 --> 01:32:25.524
or so they say.

1141
01:32:30.529 --> 01:32:32.164
A month after my mom died,
I went back.


1142
01:32:32.298 --> 01:32:34.934
It was the first time
I had been there in decades.


1143
01:32:35.067 --> 01:32:36.902
Mm, I sat there
trying to figure out


1144
01:32:37.036 --> 01:32:38.570
if I did it
'cause of faith...


1145
01:32:41.173 --> 01:32:43.175
if I just wanted
to feel her again.


1146
01:32:44.610 --> 01:32:46.545
-Did it work?
-Huh!


1147
01:32:49.615 --> 01:32:51.717
-[sighs]
-We're all alone, Samuel.


1148
01:32:54.486 --> 01:32:55.788
Do you think he did it?

1149
01:32:59.858 --> 01:33:01.727
My dad's
never lied to me before.


1150
01:33:04.029 --> 01:33:05.698
There's always a first time.

1151
01:33:09.168 --> 01:33:10.736
