1152
01:33:13.672 --> 01:33:15.741
I'm understandably
confused...


1153
01:33:16.375 --> 01:33:17.643
how-- how--

1154
01:33:20.179 --> 01:33:23.248
how a man
who worked so hard...


1155
01:33:24.149 --> 01:33:26.752
to forgive the man
that killed his wife...


1156
01:33:28.455 --> 01:33:30.255
who welcomed him
into the church...


1157
01:33:32.558 --> 01:33:33.926
and by all accounts...

1158
01:33:35.428 --> 01:33:36.962
tried to save his soul...

1159
01:33:39.498 --> 01:33:40.766
would suddenly kill him.

1160
01:33:46.505 --> 01:33:47.773
[sighs]

1161
01:33:48.240 --> 01:33:49.508
You have to ask him.

1162
01:33:51.510 --> 01:33:52.778
I did.

1163
01:33:54.580 --> 01:33:56.582
I didn't believe
the lie he told me.


1164
01:34:01.120 --> 01:34:02.354
[sighs]

1165
01:34:03.222 --> 01:34:06.091
If you know something
different than what he said...


1166
01:34:06.992 --> 01:34:09.695
it is your moral obligation
to do something.


1167
01:34:14.066 --> 01:34:15.134
He loves you...

1168
01:34:16.469 --> 01:34:17.870
you know that.

1169
01:34:19.472 --> 01:34:20.739
A lot.

1170
01:34:23.909 --> 01:34:25.277
He's being
arraigned tomorrow.


1171
01:34:29.248 --> 01:34:30.582
I, uh...

1172
01:34:32.551 --> 01:34:33.520
I wanted you to know.

